WEBVTT

12:35.880 --> 12:38.580 line:80%
You filthy old hag who deserves
to be buried with no coffin!

12:38.580 --> 12:40.040 line:80%
Not only do you have a wicked tongue,

12:40.040 --> 12:41.900 line:80%
you don't even do good deeds
for your grandson.

12:41.900 --> 12:43.550 line:80%
Aren't you afraid the King of Hell

12:43.550 --> 12:44.740 line:80%
will rip your tongue out after you die?

12:44.740 --> 12:46.350 line:80%
How am I wicked?
